synopsis.value: In what used to be a crypt or knight’s hall, there’s now a large portal, and a sort of console used to control it. As we arrive, Kith'rak Voss jumps through. A lone Gith is left behind to close the portal behind him and destroy as many of the following intruders as she can before being inevitably killed. The lone Gith is about to destroy the console when she sees us. At this point, the Butcher and his remaining followers also arrive on the scene.
